  "Basics/B2/proof/routes-b4-verified.txt": "# B4 Route Verification ‚Äî captured 2026-06-22T18:01:32Z\n\n## Server startup\n\n```bash\ncd $REPO_ROOT/tasks/Basics/B4\nsource .venv/bin/activate\nuvicorn app.main:app --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8000\n```\n\n## OpenAPI paths (GET /openapi.json)\n\n```bash\ncurl -s http://127.0.0.1:8000/openapi.json | python3 -c \"import sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print('\n'.join(sorted(d.get('paths',{}).keys())))\"\n```\n\n```\n/balance\n/transactions\n```\n\n## GET /transactions\n\n```bash\ncurl -s -w '\nHTTP_STATUS: %{http_code}\n' http://127.0.0.1:8000/transactions\n```\n\n```\n[]\nHTTP_STATUS: 200\n```\n\n## GET /balance\n\n```bash\ncurl -s -w '\nHTTP_STATUS: %{http_code}\n' http://127.0.0.1:8000/balance\n```\n\n```\n{\"balance\":\"0.00\"}\nHTTP_STATUS: 200\n```\n\n## POST /transactions (credit)\n\n```bash\ncurl -s -w '\nHTTP_STATUS: %{http_code}\n' -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/transactions \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"amount\": \"150.00\", \"type\": \"credit\", \"description\": \"B2 route verification deposit\"}'\n```\n\n```\n{\"id\":1,\"amount\":\"150.00\",\"type\":\"credit\",\"description\":\"B2 route verification deposit\"}\nHTTP_STATUS: 201\n```\n\n## POST /transactions (debit)\n\n```bash\ncurl -s -w '\nHTTP_STATUS: %{http_code}\n' -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/transactions \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"amount\": \"25.00\", \"type\": \"debit\", \"description\": \"B2 route verification withdrawal\"}'\n```\n\n```\n{\"id\":2,\"amount\":\"25.00\",\"type\":\"debit\",\"description\":\"B2 route verification withdrawal\"}\nHTTP_STATUS: 201\n```\n\n## GET /balance (after mutations)\n\n```bash\ncurl -s -w '\nHTTP_STATUS: %{http_code}\n' http://127.0.0.1:8000/balance\n```\n\n```\n{\"balance\":\"125.00\"}\nHTTP_STATUS: 200\n```\n\n## GET /transactions (after mutations)\n\n```bash\ncurl -s -w '\nHTTP_STATUS: %{http_code}\n' http://127.0.0.1:8000/transactions\n```\n\n```\n[{\"id\":1,\"amount\":\"150.00\",\"type\":\"credit\",\"description\":\"B2 route verification deposit\"},{\"id\":2,\"amount\":\"25.00\",\"type\":\"debit\",\"description\":\"B2 route verification withdrawal\"}]\nHTTP_STATUS: 200\n```\n",
